artifex (0.1.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Dependency scanner now uses SHA-1 to compare files.

  * General bugfixes in dependency scanner and pkgconfig() routine.

  * Support alternative pkg-config-like scripts (like sdl-config)

 -- Kristoffer Grönlund <kristoffer.gronlund@purplescout.se>  Sun, 06 Dec 2009 23:51:12 +0100

artifex (0.1.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Before/after clauses

  * Cache configuration between runs

  * pkg-config support

  * Handle subdirectories better

  * Color output

  * Improved dependency tracking

 -- Kristoffer Grönlund <kristoffer.gronlund@purplescout.se>  Sun, 06 Dec 2009 15:21:50 +0100

